title: Pixel data move fails to copy photos, settings, call history and more.
content:
Upgrading from a Pixel 2 to a Pixel 4a with 5G, the data move fails to copy photos, settings, call history and more.
I've tried using the data transfer cable and tried just a backup and restore method.  Neither copies photos, settings, texts, call history, etc.
category: Setting up and Personalizing your Device
